Story

Motivation: Izabella left a message to Sasha in St. Petersburg at the Lomonov.  It stated only that she was moving to the United States to raise their daughter. (One he was unaware of) The letter was dated 2001. If the child was his, she would be 24.  His search has only discovered that Izabella immigrated to Washington.  Sasha has no clue how to find her or what she looks like or even what he would do should he find her.  Harmony can be cultivated anywhere and so Sasha has chosen Seattle, just in case.
